-> First of all, for Fintech we need to know some basics of Transactions like how they communicate with each other, so there is a thing which is very common in fintech
that is Iso-8583, now let's break it! ISO is a Standard you might have heared Iso-2002 standard on Food Products it simply means that this is a standard which every one 
have to follow in order to make or built something, so Iso-8583 is just a standard which every bank or anyone needs to follow in order to communicate with each other.
